  </td> </tr>
  <tr class="en"> <td>
    Now I have begun to understand computers.
  </td> </tr>
</table>
</p>

<p>
<a name="to-present">@EM{{@Vte{{}}@KJ{{come}}@HI{{ru}}}}</a> can indicate the continuation of a process up to
the current point in time. This usage applies to any non-puntual verb.

<table class="sentence" border=0>
