    @HI{{@KJ{{private}}hairoiro@KJ{{day^book}}no@KJ{{curriculum^history^write}}wo@KJ{{read}}nde@KJ{{come}}mashita.}}
  </td> </tr>
  <tr class="en"> <td>
    Up to now I've been reading various Japanese histories.
